all this data that it has collected over the course of someone’s entire life, let’s say from when

00:15:35.191 --> 00:15:42.051
they were 13 years old right through to when they are 80, then with virtual reality and artificial

00:15:42.051 --> 00:15:49.451
intelligence it will be able to do a pretty good job of recreating a digital copy of that person.

00:15:50.421 --> 00:15:55.031
You might be able to have a conversation with a deceased loved one, you might be able

00:15:55.031 --> 00:15:59.871
to see what they would have looked like if they had had the chance to grow old, you

00:15:59.871 --> 00:16:04.771
could do almost anything with them, and it would be like they were there with you.

