In a weird way, if you have lived in a country where you haven’t really been able to leave

00:16:11.031 --> 00:16:16.851
your house, town, or city for the past few months and you have had to communicate with loved

00:16:16.851 --> 00:16:23.131
ones through things like video calls, this potential future isn’t really that different.

00:16:23.781 --> 00:16:28.371
Now, this might completely creep you out, and you might think it’s the

00:16:28.681 --> 00:16:32.921
weirdest thing in the world, but the possibilities will certainly exist.

00:16:34.001 --> 00:16:40.221
And much like it might seem strange to us that the Victorians used to have Death

00:16:40.221 --> 00:16:46.441
Portraits, and you might be baffled to think that the Toraja people keep their relatives

00:16:46.581 --> 00:16:52.401
in their house for months or years after they die, a future where at least a digital

00:16:52.411 --> 00:16:57.731
version of our loved ones remains after they pass is certainly not so far away.

